			Company Description 


			Arbutus Biopharma Corp. is a biopharmaceutical company. It focuses on discovering, developing and commercializing a cure for patients suffering from chronic HBV infection, a liver disease caused by the hepatitis B virus. The company was founded on October 6, 2005 and is headquartered in Burnaby, Can...
		


                Arbutus Biopharma Corp. is a biopharmaceutical company. It focuses on discovering, developing and commercializing a cure for patients suffering from chronic HBV infection, a liver disease caused by the hepatitis B virus. The company was founded on October 6, 2005 and is headquartered in Burnaby, Canada.
            




